    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i get that, but i dont really have time to go to the clinic right now and i've seen a lot of biohacking forums saying that loading up on it for a few weeks is how you reset your levels. if i only do it for like 4 or 6 weeks, isn't the risk of toxicity pretty low? it feels like a lot of extra work just to get a blood test for something that seems pretty straightforward.",
