      "content": "but i already have some extra vitamin d pills from my friend and they are 50,000 iu each. if i just take one every other day instead, or maybe one every three days, that would be much safer right? also if i take it with a fatty meal it absorbs better so it should work even faster. tell me what you think is the best way to dose it if i decide to go ahead with this.",
